  1,"Forty Hadith of Shah Waliullah Dehlawi","চল্লিশ হাদিস শাহ ওয়ালিউল্লাহ দেহলভি","Forty Hadith of Shah Waliullah Dehlawi","Forty Hadith of Shah Waliullah Dehlawi","Quarante Hadiths de Shah Waliullah Dehlawi","Empat Puluh Hadits Shah Waliullah Dehlawi","Сорок хадисов Шаха Валиуллы Дехлави","Kırk Hadis - Şah Veliyyullah Dehlevi","چالیس احادیث شاہ ولی اللہ دہلوی",1,40
